9. **Error Handling:** The parser must be able to handle anomalies and errors in the data without crashing or producing incorrect results.

10. **Data Privacy:** Depending on the source of the data, privacy concerns might restrict access to or usage of gender information.

By identifying these potential difficulties beforehand, one can prepare strategies to overcome them and ensure an accurate count of female individuals in the datatable.
